data.name: Error_UnrecognizedRQName
data.value: Unrecognized Refactor Qualified Name.
data.comment: - internal error if something goes wrong between VS and Cider when communicating via Refactoring Qualified Names from VSIP.

data.name: Error_UnsupportedRootRelativePath
data.value: Project does not support paths relative to the root application directory. Remove the leading '/' qualifier from the '{0}' path to correct the problem.

data.name: Error_UnterminatedCharacterData
data.value: The end of the CDATA block was not found. CDATA blocks are terminated with the characters ']]>'.
data.comment: -badly formed '<[CDATA[ ...]]>' construct

data.name: Error_UnterminatedComment
data.value: The end of the comment was not found. Comments are terminated with the characters '-->'.
data.comment: -badly formed comment block

data.name: Error_UnterminatedProcessingInstruction
data.value: The end of the processing instruction was not found. Processing instructions are terminated with the characters '?>'.
data.comment: -badly formed processing instruction

data.name: Error_UnterminatedString
data.value: The end of the string was not found. The string is terminated with a ({0}) character.
data.comment: badly formed string

data.name: Error_UnterminatedXmlText
data.value: The end of the text block was not found. The character data must be included in an element.
data.comment: -sequence of text that is not bound by <..>

data.name: Error_UsingNamespaceNotFoundInAssembly
data.value: Undefined namespace. The 'using' URI refers to a namespace '{0}' that could not be found.
data.comment: - UA_REVIEW;mmalone. Also, don't localize 'using'. - should be warning (ChuckJ) - Used a namespace and assembly, but NS not found in assembly

data.name: Error_WrongFrameworkLoaded
data.value: The version of the .NET Framework that is installed is not the correct version for this version of $(VSGeneralBrandName). Some features of the XAML designer may not be available. Repair $(VSGeneralBrandName) to correct this problem.
data.comment: VSGeneralBrandName is not literal, and is substituted at build time.

data.name: Error_XamlAttributeOnlyValidOnRoot
data.value: The attribute '{0}' from the XAML namespace is only accepted on the root element.
data.comment: -attributes such as x:Class

data.name: Error_XDataCanHaveOnlyOneElement
data.value: An XData element in the XAML namespace can have only one child element.
